<plot>Three related women have summer romances in this drama. The first (Joanna Cassidy) has recently been deserted by her husband. When an old college beau (Barry Bostwick) shows up, sparks fly. Meanwhile her sister (Linda Purl) is wrestling with a rock star (Rick Moses). And finally her daughter (Tracy Nelson) goes abroad and gets involved with a non-English speaking young man (Sasha Mitchell).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?436062</url></doc>
